forward, although we have no clear mandate as yet," he said,
adding the union hoped this would be rationalized before the
London conference on March 11.
</P>
<P>
Last month farmers offered 1.5 million hectares of commercial
farm land that would be used for the settling of landless
peasants under the poverty alleviation program.
</P>
<P>
