National People's Congress Standing Committee, visited a
painting exhibition at the China Art Gallery here today.
</P>
<P>
During his visit, Qiao spoke highly of "Vagrants", a painting with
the theme of patriotism, by Chinese painter Jiang Zhaohe.
</P>
<P>
The exhibition features 140 Chinese paintings collected by the
Palace Museum and the art gallery.
</P>
