The seminar is sponsored by the municipal government of
Tianjin and the local Nankai University, Zhou Enlai's alma mater.
</P>
<P>
At the same time, an exhibition marking the centenary of the
birth of Zhou opened in Chengdu, capital of southwest China's
Sichuan Province.
</P>
<P>
On display at the exhibition, titled the "Life of Zhou Enlai",
are over 210 photographs and 137 articles.  
