here today at the Great Hall of the People.
</P>
<P>
Set up on the occasion of the first anniversary of the death of
senior leader Deng, the institute aims to promote study and
research into Deng's thought in the spheres of politics, economy,
culture, education, science and technology, and military and
diplomatic affairs, with an eye to applying his ideas in the
course of building a socialist market economy in China, the
sponsors noted.
