</P>
<P>
Liberation:
</P>
<P>
-- The black series of the Israeli intelligence Mossad
continued one after another, as another of its operation misfired,
this time in Berne, the Swiss capital, where one Mossad agent was
arrested this week. Israel and Switzerland originally decided to
keep the affair secret, but the officials of Mossad broke the news
out in order to force the resignation of their chief.
</P>
