<HEADLINE> Enqvist Enters Advanta Quarter-finals </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Washington, February 26 (Xinhua) -- Thomas Engvist of Sweden
sailed into the quarter-finals of the Advanta Tennis Championships
with a three-set victory over German Marcello Graca at
Philadelphia on Thursday.
</P>
<P>
Enqvist, who lost the first set 4-6, managed to take the second
after winning the tie-breaker. He totally outplayed Graca in the
third set by winning 13 straight points to wrap up the match 4-6,
7-6 (7-2), 6-2.
</P>
<P>
In other second-round matches on Thursday, Jeff Tarango beat
fellow American Jonathan Stark 6-2, 6-7 (4-7), 6-3, Grant Stafford
of South Africa eliminated paul Haarhuis of the Netherlands 6-3,
6-4. 
</P>
</TEXT>
